itiates a specific task or process, and the system requires user input about how or whether to proceed.","pos":[1196,1323]},{"content":"Dialogs are modal and require that users interact with the controls in the dialog before they can return to the parent page.","pos":[1324,1448]},{"content":"Dialogs also can have multiple sizes.","pos":[1449,1486]},{"content":"Selection of a dialog size is subjective, and will vary, depending on the form elements that you've modeled on the dialog.","pos":[1487,1609]},{"content":"The sizes are as follows:","pos":[1610,1635]},{"content":"<bpt id=\"p1\">**</bpt>Small<ept id=\"p1\">**</ept> – This size is a one-column-wide dialog.","pos":[1641,1691],"source":"**Small** – This size is a one-column-wide dialog."},{"content":"If your dialog contains a relatively small amount of content (all simple fields, and no wide tables or other wide elements), you can probably use this size.","pos":[1692,1848]},{"content":"<bpt id=\"p1\">**</bpt>Medium<ept id=\"p1\">**</ept> – This size is a two-column-wide dialog.","pos":[1853,1904],"source":"**Medium** – This size is a two-column-wide dialog."},{"content":"If your dialog contains more content than can comfortably fit within a small dialog, but a full-width dialog isn’t required, you should use this size.","pos":[1905,2055]},{"content":"<bpt id=\"p1\">**</bpt>Large<ept id=\"p1\">**</ept> – This size is a three-column-wide dialog.","pos":[2060,2112],"source":"**Large** – This size is a three-column-wide dialog."},{"content":"If your dialog contains more content than can comfortably fit within a medium dialog, but a full-width dialog isn’t required, you should use this size.","pos":[2113,2264]},{"content":"<bpt id=\"p1\">**</bpt>Full<ept id=\"p1\">**</ept> – A large dialog is nearly the full width of the browser viewport.","pos":[2269,2344],"source":"**Full** – A large dialog is nearly the full width of the browser viewport."},{"content":"Its size varies, depending on the viewport width, and it will always be the largest dialog size option.","pos":[2345,2448]},{"content":"Use this size if your dialog has a lot of wide elements, or if it requires an unusually large amount of horizontal space.","pos":[2449,2570]},{"content":"For more detail about the various dialog sizes, see the table in the appendix of this article, under “Selecting the correct dialog size.”","pos":[2572,2709]},{"content":"We strongly recommend that you review that table.","pos":[2710,2759]},{"content":"Five patterns are described in this document:","pos":[2760,2805]},{"content":"<bpt id=\"p1\">**</bpt>Dialog<ept id=\"p1\">**</ept> – This is the basic dialog pattern.","pos":[2811,2857],"source":"**Dialog** – This is the basic dialog pattern."},{"content":"If you don’t have a reason to use one of the other two patterns, you should use this one.","pos":[2858,2947]},{"content":"<bpt id=\"p1\">**</bpt>Dialog w/tabs<ept id=\"p1\">**</ept> – This is a more specific version of the Dialog pattern.","pos":[2952,3026],"source":"**Dialog w/tabs** – This is a more specific version of the Dialog pattern."},{"content":"It incorporates a Tab control in the dialog.","pos":[3027,3071]},{"content":"You can also optionally provide a header for the Tab, and also a footer.","pos":[3072,3144]},{"pos":[3149,3292],"content":"<bpt id=\"p1\">**</bpt>Dialog w/FastTabs<ept id=\"p1\">**</ept> – This closely resembles the Dialog w/tabs pattern but uses FastTabs instead of regular tabs to organize the information.","source":"**Dialog w/FastTabs** – This closely resembles the Dialog w/tabs pattern but uses FastTabs instead of regular tabs to organize the information."},{"pos":[3297,3434],"content":"<bpt id=\"p1\">**</bpt>Dialog w/double tabs<ept id=\"p1\">**</ept> – This closely resembles the Dialog w/tabs pattern but has a second Tab control immediately after the first one.","source":"**Dialog w/double tabs** – This closely resembles the Dialog w/tabs pattern but has a second Tab control immediately after the first one."},{"co