xt<ept id=\"p1\">](https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/dynamics365/operations/dev-itpro/user-interface/fill-text-subpattern)</ept>","source":"[Fill Text](https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/dynamics365/operations/dev-itpro/user-interface/fill-text-subpattern)"},{"pos":[7253,7266],"content":"UX guidelines","linkify":"UX guidelines","nodes":[{"content":"UX guidelines","pos":[0,13]}]},{"content":"The verification checklist shows the steps for manually verifying that the form complies with UX guidelines.","pos":[7267,7375]},{"content":"This checklist doesn't include any guidelines that will be enforced automatically through the development environment.","pos":[7376,7494]},{"content":"Open the form in the browser, and walk through these steps.","pos":[7495,7554]},{"content":"<bpt id=\"p1\">**</bpt>Standard form<ept id=\"p1\">**</ept> <bpt id=\"p2\">**</bpt>guidelines:<ept id=\"p2\">**</ept>","pos":[7555,7588],"source":"**Standard form** **guidelines:**"},{"pos":[7594,7813],"content":"Standard form guidelines have been consolidated into the Microsoft Dynamics AX <bpt id=\"p1\">[</bpt>General Form Guidelines<ept id=\"p1\">](https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/dynamics365/operations/dev-itpro/user-interface/general-form-guidelines)</ept>document.","source":"Standard form guidelines have been consolidated into the Microsoft Dynamics AX [General Form Guidelines](https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/dynamics365/operations/dev-itpro/user-interface/general-form-guidelines)document."},{"pos":[7815,7837],"content":"<bpt id=\"p1\">**</bpt>Dialog guidelines:<ept id=\"p1\">**</ept>","source":"**Dialog guidelines:**"},{"content":"Focus should be in the first editable field in the dialog box when the dialog box is first opened.","pos":[7843,7941]},{"pos":[7950,8033],"content":"<bpt id=\"p1\">**</bpt>Exception:<ept id=\"p1\">**</ept> If the dialog is read-only, focus should be on the <bpt id=\"p2\">**</bpt>Close<ept id=\"p2\">**</ept> button.","source":"**Exception:** If the dialog is read-only, focus should be on the **Close** button."},{"pos":[8038,8091],"content":"A dialog must have a <bpt id=\"p1\">**</bpt>main instruction<ept id=\"p1\">**</ept> at the top.","source":"A dialog must have a **main instruction** at the top."},{"content":"A final period should not be included if the instruction is a statement.","pos":[8100,8172]},{"content":"If the instruction is a question, a question mark should be included.","pos":[8173,8242]},{"content":"A secondary instruction to the user can optionally be included, and it should present additional information that will help the user understand or use the dialog box.","pos":[8247,8413]},{"content":"The secondary instruction should consist of a complete sentence in sentence case and should have end punctuation.","pos":[8414,8527]},{"pos":[8532,8570],"content":"A dialog must have a <bpt id=\"p1\">**</bpt>content<ept id=\"p1\">**</ept> area.","source":"A dialog must have a **content** area."},{"content":"For editable dialogs:","pos":[8575,8596]},{"content":"The content area should contain only the controls that are required in order to complete the task.","pos":[8605,8703]},{"content":"Constrained input controls, such as selection lists, check boxes, radio buttons, and command links, should be used to avoid validation errors.","pos":[8712,8854]},{"content":"Reasonable default values for each input should be provided whenever possible.","pos":[8863,8941]},{"content":"Controls should not cause another dialog to appear during validation.","pos":[8950,9019]},{"content":"Warning messages for validation issues should be displayed in a message bar as soon as possible.","pos":[9032,9128]},{"content":"For read-only dialogs:","pos":[9133,9155]},{"content":"The content area should only contain controls that are non-editable or only allow the user to switch the data is displayed, such as a view selector.","pos":[9164,9312]},{"content":"Programmatically changing the value of a field should not cause validation errors.","pos":[9321,9403]}